📘 Test Strategy Document – Admin Tool
1. Document Overview
Objective

This document outlines the test strategy for the Admin Tool used for authoring, configuring, and publishing artifacts such as Questions, Checklists, Templates, and Vendor configurations. The goal is to ensure high quality, reliability, and scalability of the system across UI, API, and data layers.

